PollingClient - class de.buw.medien.cscw.sensation.client.desktop.PollingClient.
PollingClient
This client request sensor values from the GatewayXMLRPC and
use this data to give feedback.
Represents the values of a movement sensor in the volume and
a small animation.
Able to:
- execute exec commands (execute AppleScripts, if the operating system is a mac: start and stop the iTunes; set, increase and decrease Volume)
- change the speed of the animation
